Title: Fixed possible exception during activation when files are modified while activating
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.4.0p9
Date: 1499674099
Class: fix

When activating changes via WATO it is packing the current configuration in so called sync
snapshots. In case the files are modified while being packed an error occured preventing
the whole activation process. This could especially happen in environments with a larger
number of active GUI users.
